<p
className={`w-element ch7xx7z c1v90cn6 c115nxwc c1lwn44j c1fjww6l`}>
{"Seamless gutters are just that, seamless. The way this is accomplished is the gutter machine runs the metal in a way that it can be used with a hidden bracket. The bracket supports the gutter and is screwed into the fascia board ensuring it will not pop loose over time."}
</p>
